detailResultFields.label: Course Section Definition Public Notes
detailResultFields.value: Prerequisites: FNEL 201 in the same language. An intermediate level study of henqeminem, the traditional language of the Musqueam people. The location of the class is on the Musqueam Reserve at the Musqueam Community Center, 6735 Salish Drive, Vancouver, B.C. For further information, please contact cis.program@ubc.ca For interested students, please register on the waitlist as we will be conducting a pre-requisite check and notifying students that are accepted into the course. Please note that registering on the waitlist does not guarantee that students will get into the course.
